DocAttribute.Name: BottomXDim
DocAttribute.Documentation: The extent of the bottom line measured along the implicit x-axis.

DocAttribute.Name: TopXDim
DocAttribute.Documentation: The extent of the top line measured along the implicit x-axis.

DocAttribute.Name: YDim
DocAttribute.Documentation: The extent of the distance between the parallel bottom and top lines measured along the implicit y-axis.

DocAttribute.Name: TopXOffset
DocAttribute.Documentation: Offset from the beginning of the top line to the bottom line, measured along the implicit x-axis.
